\begin_inset Formula \[
\mathbf{E}\left(0,t\right)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\mathbf{A}_{+}+\mathbf{A}_{-}\\
i\left(\mathbf{A}_{-}-\mathbf{A}_{+}\right)\\
0\end{array}\right)e^{-i\omega t}\]

