\begin_inset Formula $I_{1}\simeq I_{2}$
\end_inset 

.
 La expresión final es 
\begin_inset Formula \[
I=2I_{2}\left(1+\cos\left(\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}\frac{xd}{D}-kd\sin\alpha\right)\right)\]

\end_inset 


