\noun on 
Fresnel:
\begin_inset Formula \begin{eqnarray*}
\hat{u} & \simeq & u_{0}e^{ikz}\left(1-1-ik\frac{kR^{2}}{2z}+\ldots\right)\\
 & = & \frac{e^{ikz}}{i\lambda z}u_{0}\pi R^{2}\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset 

 
\noun default 
